---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
; <code>-a</code>
: Output all.
; <code>-b, --brief</code>
: Be brief about it.
; <code>--verbose</code>
: Talk a great deal.
; <code>-f FILE</code>
: Read input from FILE.

The description may also start on the next line:

; <code>--output=FILE</code>
: Write output to FILE instead of standard output.
